title: Pinus sylvestris 'Clumber Hump' 3/2022 Scotch F2-
description: Pinus sylvestris 'Clumber Hump' 3/2022 Scotch F2- (Scotch Pine) Dwarf Scotch Pine, Size at 10 years: 1x2ft., green, USDA Hardiness Zone 3, Michigan Bloom Month -, In Garden Bed F2 for 23 MONTHS (Stanley). Planted in 2020. Stanley & Sons: A dwarf spreading form of Scotch Pine. Leaves thick and green. Stems close and spreading. Very tight bunched plant. Photo by F.D.Richards, SE Michigan.
